transcript:
Customer: Haan bhai Pawar ji.
Executive: Hello.
Customer: Sir Namaskar.
Executive: Hello.
Customer: Namaskar sir Namaskar.
Executive: Ji ji ji Namaskar. Sir baat hui kya nahi hui isse aapki?
Customer: Baat to hui process mein hai sab cheeze.
Executive: De di hai na aapne detail sari?
Customer: Sab kuch haan.
Executive: Okay okay main baat kar leta hu sir main karta hu jaldi karwata hu. Haan theek hai sir.
Customer: Theek hai okay.
